data.text:
What’s Your Color?

The Cover Girlz specializes in making great events extraordinary events!

For weddings, special occasions, corporate events, banquets, and more; we offer our clients chair covers, satin or organza sashes in a wide variety of colors, and knot options that will give you the perfect look! Call us at (216) 214-2259 or drop us a line using our online inquiry form. We’ll follow-up with you promptly.

Curious what difference chair covers could make? Try our iDo Decor Options App!
